      "date": "2013-12-18 07:01:24.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nThe log showed that \"01:09:41:wtm-21vm3: error: get_param: /proc/{fs,sys}/{lnet,lustre}/osd-*/lustre-M*/mntdev: Found no match\". I don't know why it didn't find mntdev on mds1.\n\nLet me retest it.",
